Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我叫苏伊露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我们一族的代表前来祝贺阿隆大人复活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  妖精的通路已经打开  我便立刻赶来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:00:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是因为赶路太匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有些疲惫  想稍微躺一会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果不知不觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被涨潮的海浪卷走  冲回了海里…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上是有潮汐涨落的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次祝贺您的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被吩咐今后要侍奉阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来侍奉？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就加加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.34,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  只有皮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树枝很潮湿  火生不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冲到海岸上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海岸上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  毛皮中充满了油脂  应该很易燃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很易燃呢  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请  苏伊露小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味  这只肯定是我抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说螃蟹早吃腻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说美味的是酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩  不要喝太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然又要像之前一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  摩尔嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.72,0:06:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不长教训的人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  差不多回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩  回去了哦  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要喝哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  适可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人  是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得阿隆大人刚允许我在身边侍奉您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却不得不向您请求暂时离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  理由说出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服…重要的衣服…找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  对我们一族来说  那件衣服是仅次于生命重要的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有它的话我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一生都回不了故乡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别哭了  我们也帮你一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安珑小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起找的话很快就会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  那件衣服是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那个…说是衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实刚好是我这样大小的海豹皮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆  你知道什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  多么微不足道的事都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道什么的话请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  阿隆大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为我说生不起火才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然回不了故乡会很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一生都会在阿隆大人身边努力侍奉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可喜可贺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  奥伽姆  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性海豹妖精会嫁给夺走她衣服的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且既然烧掉了就不能还给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根三叉戟好帅气  让我看看让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不喜欢的食物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先喝点热牛奶吗  喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫苏伊露  请…请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这是肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要在意  我也想帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  像这样用手指圈成一个圆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  像这样放在奶牛的乳头上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力挤就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手指圈成一个圆…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太紧张  温柔一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挤奶让奶牛生气  洗衣服又洗得一身泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  谁都有失败的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错  别在意别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我还算不上不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普布鲁克斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是盖尔那些家伙抢走的马车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  那些家伙就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我实在是太走运了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去召集士兵  找到他们的基地并发动突袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我直言  我们的任务是前线的侦查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该先回本部报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去报告的话  肯定会被其他人抢走功劳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样的话就违反命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不知道随机应变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样你才一直爬不上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的话就乖乖地去召集士兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  帝国士兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  有报告说南边的溪谷附近发现敌人踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到这里来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南边的溪谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是  吊桥那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南边溪谷的吊桥是连接城堡和岛屿南部的通道之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城堡和吊桥之间的森林就相当于城墙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反对于敌人  森林易于藏身  也可以说是很有利的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在森林中迎击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这前方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻率  太轻率了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别落后了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下令撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气打倒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对我指手画脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去只会增加伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先撤退才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开  别挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普布鲁克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退  快撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓箭队掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桥破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙  居然连伙伴都不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都没把彼此当作伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你居然敢顶撞上司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做了我觉得正确的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说那是正确的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把人的性命当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保佑我无论身处何种情况  都能不迷失正确的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指引我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连一同战斗的伙伴都不帮助  不互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且  不论发生什么  我都要守护他们到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以我的荣耀发誓


